        Constructor DataChannelImplFile creates a new DataChannelImplFile instance.
        Parameters:
        name - name of file channel
        transport - DataTransport object that created this channel
        attributeMap - the hashmap of config file attributes for this channel
        input - true if this is an input
        emu - emu this channel belongs to
        module - module this channel belongs to
        outputIndex - order in which module's events will be sent to this output channel (0 for first output channel, 1 for next, etc.).
        Throws:
        DataTransportException - if unable to create fifo buffer.
